trans-unit.source: Represents an extensibility element added to an <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"></xref> within an XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et extensibility-element som er lagt til en <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.OperationBinding"> </xref> i en XML-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: This class respresents an extensibility element in Web Services Description Language (WSDL) specific to HTTP.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen respresents et extensibility-element i Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) gjelder HTTP.

trans-unit.source: It specifies the relative URL of an operation using as the base the location specified by an <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.HttpAddressBinding>.
trans-unit.target: Angir den relative URL-adressen for en bruker som grunntallet plasseringen angitt av en <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.HttpAddressBinding>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.HttpAddressBinding> operasjon

trans-unit.source: For more information about specifying protocols for XML Web services, see [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices>]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om hvordan du angir protokollene for XML-webtjenester [[\<topic://cpconbuildingaspnetwebservices >]](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/01dfc27c-c68e-4910-a0aa-5e4c2a766b0c).

trans-unit.source: For more information about WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om WSDL, kan du se spesifikasjonen på http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.HttpOperationBinding"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.HttpOperationBinding"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the URL relative to the location specified by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.HttpAddressBinding"></xref>, within the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) document, of the operation supported by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.HttpOperationBinding"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir URL-adressen i forhold til plasseringen angitt av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.HttpAddressBinding"> </xref>, i Web Services Description Language (WSDL) dokument, for operasjonen støttes av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.HttpOperationBinding"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: An unencoded string representing the relative path.
trans-unit.target: En unencoded streng som representerer relativ bane.

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
